This paper deals with natural language processing and temporal relations, which are topics commonly studied in the subfield of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of multiple classifiers and integer programming also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.LG, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of text data, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
